        "timestamp": "2019-03-06 10:59:23.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\nA little longer justification on patch set #4 contents: app_helm_chart_name and app_helm_build_targets are nowhere documented (install guide i mean) so i see no point in putting them in all.yml and for sure not in application_configuration.yml - if user is not instructed how to use these then they shall not be presented them. \n\nAnd even so changing 'onap' to another value is currently unsupported so yet another reason to put them in defaults without pretending and fouling a user that they can be altered at all.\n\n+1 Verified",
        "patchset_number": 4
      },
